scenes.description: Gawr Gura introduces the 'Cable Spaghetti Collector' cable ties featuring Ebi and Bloop.
Presentation of the 'guRED and BLUera Glass Set' with illustrations by Same-anko.
Showcasing the 'Ebi-chan Plushie' and discussing its features and chat's reactions.
Detailing the 'Bonus for the Complete Set' postcard and the 'Birthday Merch Complete Set'.
